  "name": "Old Village of Hollókő and its Surroundings",
  "description": "Hollok&ouml; is an outstanding example of a deliberately preserved traditional settlement. This village, which developed mainly during the 17th and 18th centuries, is a living example of rural life before the agricultural revolution of the 20th century.",
